_sText:
I think this was my 2nd or 3rd map ever.
Fort vs fort like battle, There's a bunker in the middle of the map, And a series of non-complex and symetrical tunnels.
2 Bombsites under the map, Right next to each other as well.

High skybox so if you want low-gravity, Go for it ^^

This is the Friday, 13 January 2006 version, And will not be updated anymore, If you have an older version, Get this version.
